data.description: Very RARE opportunity! Gorgeously upgraded 4BR/2BA home centrally located atop Alpine on over 1-Acre of private, usable land w/ breathtaking VIEWS! Turnkey home, light & bright floor-plan offering both Upstairs & Downstairs separate-entry access! Each floor features its' own 2BR/ 1BA floorpan w/ upgraded kitchens, granite slab countertops & all stainless steel appliances, upgraded laminate wood flooring, all neutral beautiful interior decor w/ full-size washer/dryer hookups on each floor, 4 individually zoned temperature controls, upgraded recessed lighting, newer ceiling fans in each room, upgraded bathrooms w/ tile decor, newer vanities & much more! This is a great opportunity to own a home with a separate entry ADU whether for separate living & privacy or the potential for extra rental INCOME! The large 1.26 Acre lot features a long driveway & gives you tons off privacy & a picturesque 'park-like' backyard w/ outdoor decks & an upstairs balcony, a variety of fruit bearing trees, 'built-in’ gas BBQ w/ outdoor patio & dining area, on-site chicken 'coop' w/ room for horse boarding & other livestock. The possibilities here are practically limitless! This property is a quiet, gorgeous sanctuary with tons of room for entertaining guests and enjoying spectacular VIEWS with breathtaking sunrises by morning & sunsets every night! Tons of off-street parking & room for all of your cars & work trucks, or RV’s/ ATV’s, boats, pool, bike or ATV track & more! Ideally located just outside of town in the extremely desirable community of Alpine with easy I-8 freeway access nearby.Also nearby hiking & biking trails, neighborhood parks & playgrounds, all the local restaurants & shopping in-town and great Alpine schools for all ages! All the conveniences you could possibly need are a short distance away while you’re enjoying your own private, country oasis. What a great property!
